{"tid":1380044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[跪求文宣急入] 攻心2.0 - 開學日去學校門口派黑警濫暴傳單","createTime":"2019-07-29T02:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T18:25:30.000Z","uid":173326,"like":97,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"657350bd1e686cdc17adb5358cace460adc01623","tid":1380044,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:19:44.000Z","msg":"除左之前嘅尋親活動繼續令班狗社交受打擊，仲要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">俾佢地班仔女以佢老豆老母為恥</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em>香港教育點失敗都唔會鼓吹暴力，班狗好多都有仔女讀緊中學、小學<br />\n</em></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">心理背景：<br />\n班黑警面對市民、其他公務員嘅唾罵都視若無睹、一錯在錯，原因有二：<br />\n1. 為左令屋企人有好生活、小朋友物質條件充裕，就算自己爛面，都要埋沒良心繼續攞份狗糧。<br />\n2. 街外人點睇唔理，反正自己生活圈子都係自己友圍爐，唔會覺得孤獨。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">行動：<br />\n<em><br />\n<ins>9月2號開學日，我地打工仔同大學生一齊請假一天</ins>，於各個間中、小學門口派發黑警濫用暴力嘅海報單張，尤其係對冇防具嘅市民都打/開槍（常見於連儂牆嗰啲）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">為左真實呈現，要彩色印刷A4 size</span></span><br />\n<ins><em>派傳單唔係鼓勵遊行乜乜乜，而係傳達真相，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以唔犯法</span>。</em></span></em></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">攻效：<br />\n如果小朋友/學生收到傳單，見到自己老豆老母嘅工作就係無差別打市民、向市民開槍，令到普通市民都無辜流血，一定好受打擊，返去問老豆老母點解要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">影響：<br />\n1. <ins>令黑警眾叛親離</ins>，連親生仔女都唾棄佢地，<ins>心理崩潰</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 令佢地<ins>小朋友心理受影響</ins>，令黑警要花多啲時間處理仔女情緒問題、修補關係，<ins>影響黑警於週末遊行嘅出勤率</ins>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 仔女為佢地黑警父母嘅惡行<ins>得到報應，警惕世人唔好為虎作倀、助紂為虐</ins>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<em>事前籌備：<br />\n1. 繼續整理過去6月至今嘅濫暴圖片，並持續收集嚟緊可能發生嘅濫暴素材。<br />\n2. 由於大量彩色列印需時，現時可以先行印刷已發生、fact check嘅濫用暴力素材，下次發夢亦可以先行派發測試反應。</em></strong></span>"},{"pid":"953946372d85ce631060ab331f40b4c776a1e727","tid":1380044,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:26:21.000Z","msg":"而家要開始籌備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764a84ae1f2bac9993f2afb0f5c31791b6fa2a6b","tid":1380044,"uid":285774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:28:01.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"23b4d0686c567873bd790f330990ea5d2be133f0","tid":1380044,"uid":145292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:28:38.000Z","msg":"長洲一定要"},{"pid":"c4d8de52d8d071a11e3d3bf09191d7535a0e24d9","tid":1380044,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:29:49.000Z","msg":"唔該傳去文宣tg group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587cbfa8608687c26dd340885b68662f4cc5fff5","tid":1380044,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4d8de52d8d071a11e3d3bf09191d7535a0e24d9","tid":1380044,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:29:49.000Z","msg":"唔該傳去文宣tg group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f6859f88879e775fb8fb23262f17d280387c43","tid":1380044,"uid":194069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:32:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c437e56557f15bd6d97afa7d9067300341f07055","tid":1380044,"uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:38:39.000Z","msg":"放學先派啦<br />\n<br />\n返學時派咪比學校沒收晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a19462aef822b7b9955838e2c74f274