":"2019-07-29T04:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ff31ec946fab76f4b83bc9ddebe86b5f63ba65","tid":1380044,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f966d07a737ccb2e6bd4b583f117840f7c3fce56","tid":1380044,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c877ece7f529e4227bd3562169e345bb7e9420d7","tid":1380044,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:14:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>全世界前後排都要買高防護嘅頭盔！</ins></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">728見到狗嘅子彈已經升級，鐵盾都打得穿，工地、單車頭盔更加防唔到</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>電單車頭盔要買snell安全標準嘅，聽講可以擋到時速500公里嘅氣槍</strong></span></ins><br />\n安全規格詳細睇：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ultimatemotorcycling.com/2013/04/08/motorcycle-helmet-standards-explained-dot-ece-22-05-snell/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fultimatemotorcycling.com%2F2013%2F04%2F08%2Fmotorcycle-helmet-standards-explained-dot-ece-22-05-snell%2F&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67QKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=9df3fe09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ultimatemotorcycling.com/2013/04/08/motorcycle-helmet-standards-explained-dot-ece-22-05-snell/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[多圖]純防護裝備：頭盔、盾</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372308\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372308</a>"},{"pid":"802a007413a16ccbc96aa85aa178913cbd5ae5bf","tid":1380044,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/n